                	<script type="text/javascript">
                		function validateSearchbox(form_name,search_name)
                		{
                            /*addons for deleting lastloc cookie*/
                           var name = 'lastloc';
   
                           var expiresz = "";
                           
                                var date = new Date();
                                date.setTime(date.getTime() - (3600*24*60*60*1000) );
                                expiresz = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
                            
                            
                           document.cookie = name + '=; expires=' + expiresz + '; path=/';
                            /*end addons*/
                            
                			var Ntt = document.getElementById(search_name);
                			if(Ntt.value=="" || ((typeof dynamicSettingsObj.searchTextDefault !== 'undefined') && Ntt.value.toLowerCase()==dynamicSettingsObj.searchTextDefault.toLowerCase())){
                                Ntt.value = dynamicSettingsObj.searchTextDefault;
                				return false;
                			}
                			return true;
                		}
                		
                		if (typeof dynamicSettingsObj.searchTextDefault !== 'undefined') {
                            $('#Ntt').focus(function(){
                                var nttdefault = dynamicSettingsObj.searchTextDefault;
                                if(this.value.toLowerCase()==nttdefault.toLowerCase()){
                  					this.value = '';
                   					
                    			}
                            
                            }).blur(function(){
                                if ( this.value == '' ) {
                                    this.value = dynamicSettingsObj.searchTextDefault;
                                }
                            });
                		}
                        //onclick event of anchor type button
                        
                        $('#searchGo').click(function(e){
                            e.preventDefault();
                            var nttsubmit = document.getElementById('nttsubmit');
                            nttsubmit.click();
                        });


                	</script>

dynamicSettingsObj.cvalue = "Category";

function redirecToCart_CheckoutStandAlone(page){
	var date = new Date();
	if(page == 'checkout'){
		var cname = "sc_scCheckout";

		var cvalue = dynamicSettingsObj.cvalue;

		date.setTime(date.getTime()+(2*24*60*60*1000));
		var cexpires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
		document.cookie = cname+"="+cvalue+cexpires+"; path=/";

		window.parent.location.href = dynamicSettingsObj.redirecToCart_CheckoutStandAlone;

	}
}

function refreshCheckoutStandAlone(item_count){
	if(item_count > 0){
		$('a#cartButtonCheckout').removeClass('cartButtonCheckout cartButtonCheckoutDisabled').addClass('cartButtonCheckout');
    $('#Cart .cell1').css('width','210px');
    $('a#cartButton').addClass('cartItem');

    $('a#cartButtonCheckout').live('click', function(){
			redirecToCart_CheckoutStandAlone('checkout');
		});
	}
	else{
		$('a#cartButtonCheckout').removeClass('cartButtonCheckout cartButtonCheckoutDisabled').addClass('cartButtonCheckoutDisabled');
		$('#Cart .cell1').css('width','118px');
    $('a#cartButton').removeClass('cartItem');

    $('a#cartButtonCheckout').unbind('click');
	}
}

$(document).ready(function() {
	//cart hover
	$.cookie('isClickedAddPromoCode', 'false', {path:'/'});
	$('.cartButtonCheckoutDisabled').hover(function(){
		if(getCookie('item_count') < 1)
			$('.noItemOnCart').stop(true, true).slideToggle(100);
	});

	//jcw custom function
	$.fn.jcwFadeIn = function(t){
		$('a#cartButton').removeClass('cartButton').addClass('cartButtonActive');
		if(typeof t != 'undefined')
			return $(this).fadeIn(t);
		else
			return $(this).fadeIn();
	}

	$.fn.jcwFadeOut = function(t){
		$('a#cartButton').removeClass('cartButtonActive').addClass('cartButton');
		if(typeof t != 'undefined')
			return $(this).fadeOut(t);
		else
			return $(this).fadeOut();
	}

    function addToCart() {	    
        getItemCount();
        getOrderItems();
        loadTopCertonaAjax();
		run_promo_burst();

        // window.location.hash = "CartSnapin";
        window.scroll(0, 0);
    }

    function outOfStock(stockPfName, stockProducts) {
		// out-of-stock
		$("#OutOfStockBtn:hidden").click();

		// Omniture Tagging
		s.pageName = "Out of Stock:'" + stockPfName + "'";
		s.channel = "Out of Stock";
		s.prop3 = "Out of Stock";
		s.events = "event6,event16";
		s.products = stockProducts;
		var s_code = s.t();
		if (s_code) {
			document.write(s_code);
		}
    }

    $('.pgrid').live('click', function(e) {
                $("#CartActive").jcwFadeIn();
                window.scroll(0, 0);
		e.preventDefault();
	    var this_parent = $(this).parents('form.formgrid');

		var date = new Date();
		var cname = "v35";
		var cvalue = "1";
		date.setTime(date.getTime()+(2*24*60*60*1000));
		var cexpires = "; expires="+date.toGMTString();
		document.cookie = cname + "=" + cvalue + cexpires + "; path=/";

		var data = "snap=1";
		data += "&" + this_parent.serialize();
		
		// check if mao add to cart was clicked
		if ( $(this).attr('offer_price') ){
			data += "&offer_price=" + $(this).attr('offer_price'); 
		}
		
		data += "&t=" + Math.floor(Math.random() * new Date());
		document.cookie = "addCartLastUrl="+document.URL+"; path=/";
		
    	if (checkInventory == true) {
			$.ajax({
				type: 'GET',
				data: data,
				timeout: 1000*30,
				url: '/additem',
				complete: function(jqXHR, status) {
					if (status == 'timeout') {
						$.get("/additem", data + "&stco=1", function(data) {
							addToCart();
							return true;
						});
					}
				},
				success: function(data) {
					if (trigger == 0) {
						outOfStock(this_parent.find("input[name=stockPfName]").val(), this_parent.find("input[name=stockProducts]").val());
					} else if (trigger == 1) {
						addToCart();
						return true;
					} else if (data == 'not_available') {
						outOfStock(this_parent.find("input[name=stockPfName]").val(), this_parent.find("input[name=stockProducts]").val());
					} else {
						addToCart();
						return true;
					}
				}
			});
    	} else {
    		$.get("/additem", data, function(data) {
    			addToCart();
    			return true;
    		});
    	}
    });

         $.get("/additem?snap=1&p_id="+p_id+"&qty="+qty+"&filterid="+filterid+"&year="+year+"&make="+make+"&model="+model+"&submodel="+submodel+"&+t="+Math.floor(Math.random() * new Date()),{  }, function(data) {

    function snapBasket(){
       count++;
       //$(".cartPromoCode p").remove();
       $(".cartPromoCode .promoresponse").remove();
       $('<p>').insertAfter(".cartPromoCode h1");
       //$(".cartPromoCode p").text("If you have a promotion code, enter it here:");

       }

    function getOrderItems() {
        //$.get("/basket/?template=small",{  }, function(data) {
		if(typeof ismao === 'undefined'){
			ismao = 0;
		}

            data = $.trim(data);

                //$("span.cartIco").css("background-position","-273px -36px");
            }else{
                $("#itemSpan").html("items");
                //$("span.cartIco").css("background-position","-248px -36px");
            }
            $("#itemCount").html(data);
        });
    }

    function getItemCount() {
        data = getCookie('item_count');
        if (data == null) data = 0;

        if(data == 1){
            $("#itemCount").css("color","#000000");
            $("#itemSpan").css("color","#000000");
            $("#itemSpan").html("item");
            //$("span.cartIco").css("background-position","-248px -36px");

            $("#itemCount").css("color","#ACACAC");
            $("#itemSpan").css("color","#ACACAC");
            $("#itemSpan").html("items");
            //$("span.cartIco").css("background-position","-273px -36px");
        }else{
            $("#itemSpan").html("items");
            //$("span.cartIco").css("background-position","-248px -36px");
        }

        $("#itemCount").html(data);

        refreshCheckoutStandAlone(data);
    }

			<script type="text/javascript">
	var catPartLink = "";
var oCatPartLink = JSON.parse(base64_decode(catPartLink));
vlp_partname();

function boxCatPart(args, _k){
	_class = (_k<2)?' border-bottom-grey ':'';
	str = 		'<div class="white '+_class+' ">';
	str = str + '<div class="category-title clearfix"><span></span><a class="category-title-link" href="javascript:void(0);">'+args.label+'</a></div>';
	str = str + '</div>';
	return str;
}

function boxChild(v1ChildLink, args){
	_strV2 = '';
	$.each(v1ChildLink, function(k2,v2) {
		_label = (isArrMultiExist(v2, ['key']) && isNaN(v2.key) )?v2.key: (isArrMultiExist(v2, ['category']))?v2.category:'';
		_link = (isArrMultiExist(v2, ['frontEndLink', 'url']))?v2.frontEndLink.url:'';
		_strV2 = _strV2 + '<li><a href="'+_link+'">'+_label+'</a></li>';
	});
	_html  = '<div class="category-list" style="display: none;">';
	_html += '	<div>';
	_html += '		<ol>';
	_html += _strV2;
	_html += '		</ol>';
	if (args.href!=''){
	_html += '		<a class="left-nav-see-more" href="'+args.href+'"><strong>See All</strong></a>';
	}
	_html += '	</div>';
	_html += '</div>';
	return _html;
}

function constructCatPart(arrData, level){
	var allStr = '';
	if (level==1){
		if (isArrMultiExist(arrData, ['popular'])){
			_count = arrData.popular.link.length;
			$.each(arrData.popular.link, function(k1,v1) {
				var _class = ( (_count-1)==k1)?' class="last" ':'';
				_boxCatPart = boxCatPart({'label':v1.category}, k1);
				if (isArrMultiExist(v1, ['Child', 'link'])){
					_href = ( isArrMultiExist(v1, ['frontEndLink', 'url']) ) ?v1.frontEndLink.url:'';
					allStr += '<li '+_class+'>' + _boxCatPart + boxChild(v1.Child.link, {'href':_href}) + '</li>';
				}
			});
		}
	}
	return allStr 
}

function openUL(level){
	switch (level){
		case 1:
			return '<ul class="level1" style="padding-left:5px;">';
		break;
		case 2:
			return '<ul class="level2" style="padding-left:10px;">';
		break;
		case 3:
			return '<ul class="level3" style="padding-left:15px;">';
		break;
	}	
}
function closeUL(level){
	return '</ul>';
}

function constructCatPartLeftNav(arrData, level){
	var allStr = '';

	if (isArrMultiExist(arrData, ['goBack_LevelOne', 'frontEndLink', 'url']) ) {		
		allStr += '<a href="' + arrData.goBack_LevelOne.frontEndLink.url + '">View All Categories</a>';
	}

	if (isArrMultiExist(arrData, ['link'])){
		$.each(arrData.link, function(k,v) {
			if (isArrMultiExist(v, ['frontEndLink', 'url'])){
				_label = (isArrMultiExist(v, ['category']))?v.category:'';
				_label = ( _label=='' && isArrMultiExist(v, ['key']) )?v.key:_label;
				_href = v.frontEndLink.url;
				allStr += '<li>';

				if (  _href!='no-link' && isArrMultiExist(v, ['Child'])){					
						_label = '< ' + _label;
				}

				allStr += (_href!='no-link')?'<a href="'+_href+'">'+_label+'</a>':'<span style="font-weight:bold;color:black;cursor:default;">'+_label+'</span>';
				
				if (isArrMultiExist(v, ['Child', 'link'])){
					allStr += openUL((level+1));
					allStr += constructCatPartLeftNav(v.Child, (level+1));
					allStr += closeUL((level+1));
				}
				allStr += '</li>';
			}
			else if (isArrMultiExist(v, ['type'])){
				_label = (isArrMultiExist(v, ['value']))?v.value:'';
				allStr += '<li>'+ _label +'</li>';
			}
		});
	}
	return allStr;
}

function vlp_partname(){
	if (isArrMultiExist(oCatPartLink, ['CategoryPartname', 'popular'])){
		var allStr = constructCatPart(oCatPartLink.CategoryPartname, 1);
		allStr = '<ul id="left-nav-category">'+allStr+'</ul>';
		allStr = allStr + $('#RefineProductsByv2 div.widgetMid div.mid').html();
		$('#RefineProductsByv2 div.widgetMid div.mid').html(allStr);
	}
	else if (isArrMultiExist(oCatPartLink, ['CategoryPartname', 'link'])){
		var allStr = constructCatPartLeftNav(oCatPartLink.CategoryPartname, 1);
		allStr = '<div class="container1"><ul id="left-nav-category" class="level-0">'+allStr+'</ul></div>';
		allStr = allStr + $('#RefineProductsByv2 div.widgetMid div.mid').html();
		$('#RefineProductsByv2 div.widgetMid div.mid').html(allStr);
	}	
	
	if ($('ul.level3').length){
		if ($('ul.level3 li').size()>10){
			$("ul.level3").append('<li class="seemore" style="color:black;">[+] See More</li>');
			$('ul.level3 li:gt(9):not(:last)').hide();
		}
	}
}

$('.seemore').live('click', function(){
	var origTempStr = $('ul.level3 li').last().html();
	$('ul.level3 li:gt(9):not(:last)').toggle('slow', function(){
		var tempStr = (origTempStr==='[-] See Less')?'[+] See More':'[-] See Less';
		$('ul.level3 li').last().html(tempStr); 
	});
});

$(function(){
	var shopName = "";		
	var shopId = 1;
	
	$('#left-nav-category li:nth-child(1)').children('.category-list').delay(1000).slideToggle('1000');
	if ( !( (shopName == 'truck') || (shopId==1) ) ) {
		$('#left-nav-category li:nth-child(2)').children('.category-list').delay(1000).slideToggle('1000');
	}
	
	$('.category-title').live('click', function(){
		$(this).parent('div').next('.category-list').slideToggle('1000');
		$(this).parent('.white').toggleClass('border-bottom-grey');
	});
});      
</script>

        		var results = regex.exec(url);

        		else

            function removeUserVehicleListB(mngVehiclebutId,prevvehicleSelectContainer,mngVehiclePopId,elementspecific) {

                // var el_mngVehiclebutId = document.getElementById(mngVehiclebutId);
                var el_prevvehicleSelectContainer = document.getElementById(prevvehicleSelectContainer);
                var el_mngVehiclePopId = document.getElementById(mngVehiclePopId);

                var uservehiclelist = document.formmanageVehicle;
                var removeVehiclelist = '';
                var removeVehicleLimit = Math.ceil(uservehiclelist.length / 2);
                var removeHtmlList = new Array();
                var vehicle_id;
                
                if (typeof elementspecific == 'undefined' && elementspecific!==null) {
                
                    // collect vehicle ids to be removed, based on the vehicle limit (see var removeVehicleLimit)
                    var ctr2=0;
                    for (var ctr=0;ctr<uservehiclelist.length;ctr++) {
                        if (!uservehiclelist[ctr].checked && ctr<removeVehicleLimit) {
                            removeHtmlList[ctr2] = uservehiclelist[ctr].value;
                            if (typeof vehicle_id == "undefined") {
                                vehicle_id = uservehiclelist[ctr].value;
                            } else {
                                vehicle_id = vehicle_id + ',' + uservehiclelist[ctr].value;
                            }
                            ctr2++;
                            removeVehiclelist += ((removeVehiclelist=='')?'':'*')+uservehiclelist[ctr].value;
                        }
                    }
                    
                    // request ajax to remove vehicle ids from cookie
                    $.get("/managevehicle/?status=remove&id="+vehicle_id, function(data,status){
                        if(status=="success"){
                            
                            // remove html of deleted vehicles from Managed Saved Vehicles popup

                                var el_vehicle = document.getElementById("managesv"+removeHtmlList[ctr]);

                                    el_vehicle.parentNode.removeChild(el_vehicle);
                                }
                            }
                            
                        }
                    });

                  
                    reverseStyle(el_mngVehiclePopId);

                  var vehicle_id = elementspecific;
                  var el_vehicle = document.getElementById(vehicle_id);
                          $.get("/managevehicle/?status=remove&id="+vehicle_id, {}, function(data,status){
                        		if(status=="success"){
                        			//loc_href = removeVehicleQuery(vehicle_id);

			else if(result.getLocation.country == 'AU' && aulbKillSwitch == 1){

				showLightbox(lb);

		} 
	});
} else if (getCookie('whitelbheader')) {
	wlHeader = 'whitelabelcanadaheader';

}

//show whitelabel lightbox
function showLightbox(lb){
	$.ajax({ 
		url:"/ajax/"+lb, 
		cache:false,
		success:function(data){  
			$.fancybox({
				centerOnScroll:true,
				content:data,
			});
		} 
	});
}

// fire WA tagging for whitelabel
function fireLightBoxWATagging(PName){
	s.linkTrackVars = 'pageName,channel,prop3';
	s.pageName = PName;
	s.channel = 'White Label';
	s.prop3 = 'White Label';
	var s_code = s.t();
	if (s_code) {
		document.write(s_code);
	}
}

//show whitelabel header
function showWhiteLabelHeader(wlHeader){
	$.ajax({ 
		url:"/ajax/"+wlHeader, 
		cache:false,
		success:function(data){ 
			$('body').prepend(data);
		}
	});
}
